From: Zijun Hu <zijun.hu@oss.qualcomm.com>
Date: Mon, 23 Jun 2025 19:23:48 +0800
Subject: Bluetooth: hci_qca: Enable ISO data packet RX
Patch-mainline: v6.17-rc1
Git-commit: b47c97f2ed9434ccff4efb0b08e3cc0a6c4e08c8
References: jsc#PED-14261

Enable ISO data packet RX for LE audio.

Signed-off-by: Zijun Hu <zijun.hu@oss.qualcomm.com>
Signed-off-by: Luiz Augusto von Dentz <luiz.von.dentz@intel.com>
Acked-by: Chun-Yi Lee <jlee@suse.com>
---
 drivers/bluetooth/hci_qca.c |    1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

--- a/drivers/bluetooth/hci_qca.c
+++ b/drivers/bluetooth/hci_qca.c
@@ -1264,6 +1264,7 @@ static const struct h4_recv_pkt qca_recv
 	{ H4_RECV_ACL,             .recv = qca_recv_acl_data },
 	{ H4_RECV_SCO,             .recv = hci_recv_frame    },
 	{ H4_RECV_EVENT,           .recv = qca_recv_event    },
+	{ H4_RECV_ISO,             .recv = hci_recv_frame    },
 	{ QCA_IBS_WAKE_IND_EVENT,  .recv = qca_ibs_wake_ind  },
 	{ QCA_IBS_WAKE_ACK_EVENT,  .recv = qca_ibs_wake_ack  },
 	{ QCA_IBS_SLEEP_IND_EVENT, .recv = qca_ibs_sleep_ind },
